sidebar.04ResourcesSidebar.category.PowP.message: The PowPeg App fka 2 way peg app converts BTC to RBTC and vice versa. It is secured by the powpeg protocol, which is a unique PowPeg system that secures the locked bitcoins with the same Bitcoin hashrate that establishes consensus.
